Public functions
    TranslationClass::word(void)
        This is the getter and returns the result of translation.
    
    TranslationClass::word(string)
        This is the setter and this sets the word that is translated.

    TranslationClass::TranslateWord()
        You need to call this function to translate a word;


Private functions
    TranslationClass::GetDictionaryHtml()
        This function gets a HTML of a dictionary website.

    TranslationClass::GetTranslation()
        This function process the HTML GetDictionaryHtml() got. And this gets just the part of word translation.

